summary: tonys genius isnt just in mechanics and engineering and chemistry. its also situational intelligence. why else do you think he...
body:
tonys genius isnt just in mechanics and engineering and chemistry. its also situational intelligence. why else do you think he played on black widows assumptions that hes self destructive and worthless without the suit? when he proved multiple times in the im trilogy that the suit is merely a bit of help cause he managed to think his way out of every situation hes gotten himself into?

cause they gave tony the perfect fake persona unknowingly - they saw him as a loud, egotistical reckless playboy and when he realized it it was easy for him to play the role around everyone and let them underestimate him, and he did it so well that he even tricked a top shield double agent (natasha) into thinking his fake persona is his actual self. tony stark is insanely smart you guys are just not noticing all of it

summary: I get the appeal of DCEU Stans saying because DCEU has made more money in it's first six films than the MCU made the DCEU is...
body:
I get the appeal of DCEU Stans saying because DCEU has made more money in it’s first six films than the MCU made the DCEU is more popular or more beloved or whatever. But we’re comparing an unknown Iron Man, Hulk, Cap and Thor to Superman, Batman and Wonder Woman. I mean, come on. I love the the DCEU keeps making money cause I want to keep seeing this universe. And I get that MCU stans are the worst so DCEU stans gotta take their wins where they can. It’s just a weird comparison. 

Iron Man, Hulk, IM2, TFA, Thor and Avengers (2008-2012) vs MoS, BvS, SS, WW, JL, Aquaman (2013 -2018) I sure as hell hope the first six DCEU films made more money than the first six MCU films as the popularity of CBM in theaters has changed a lot since MCU first started.
